# Line-ending policy.
#
# This package deploys Bash hook scripts that break under CRLF, so shell scripts
# are pinned to LF on every checkout regardless of a contributor's core.autocrlf
# setting. JSON (plugin manifest, hook registration, settings) and Markdown
# follow suit for consistency and to stop autocrlf churn on Windows clones.
# JSONL test fixtures are parsed line-by-line through jq and `while read`, which
# break on CRLF, so they are pinned to LF too.

*.sh    text eol=lf
*.json  text eol=lf
*.md    text eol=lf
*.jsonl text eol=lf
